pageTitle: Annual FFA Alumni Roundup scheduled for Nov. 1 | CynthianaDemocrat.com
TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {32763=Copyright © 2015, 25738=The Cynthiana Democrat | circulation@cynthianademocrat.com | 859-234-1035 P.O. Box 160, 302 Webster Avenue, Cynthiana, KY 41031 Office Hours are 8:30 a.m. to 5:00 p.m., Monday through Friday, 20082=The second annual FFA Alumni Roundup will be held Saturday, Nov. 1 at 5:30 p.m. at 976 Old Lair Rd., Cynthiana, (Harrison County School Farm). The meal will be potluck. Meat and drinks will be provided by the Harrison County FFA Chapter. Old scrap books and memorabilia will be on hand for all alumni to reminisce. Several pictures from the past will be on hand for alumni to claim and even explain.}
